SpreeSmsru
==========

Spree extension to send SMS with changing of a transaction status using web service sms.ru.

Installation
============

Add you Gemfile-file following line:
  gem 'spree_smsru', :require => 'spree_smsru', :git => 'git://github.com/sysadm/spree_smsru.git'

Run: bundle install

Classic installation:
a) rake spree_smsru:install
b) rake db:migrate

Edit config/smsru.yml

Pull requests welcome

